* install ecplise-maven plugin:
	*update-site http://m2eclipse.sonatype.org/update/
		* Maven integration for Eclipse
		* (Maven Central repository index)


* download jargs (http://jargs.sourceforge.net/)
* install the downloaded file into your local maven repos with the following command (replace $filetopath by the downloaded jar's filename)
	* mvn install:install-file -Dfile=$pathtofile -DgroupId=jargs -DartifactId=jargs -Dversion=1.0 -Dpackaging=jar -DgeneratePom=true
* update the dependencies in eclipse (might take some time)
	* project -> rightclick -> maven -> update